      "text": [
        "4663 - وَ قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَا مِنْ لَبَنٍ يُرْضَعُ بِهِ اَلصَّبِيُّ أَعْظَمَ بَرَكَةً عَلَيْهِ مِنْ لَبَنِ أُمِّهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4663 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"There is no milk with greater blessing for a child to be nursed with than the milk of his mother.\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
